================================================================================
  3X-UI panel
================================================================================
URL (direct, exposes panel to internet):
    http://{{ ansible_facts.default_ipv4.address | default(ansible_facts.fqdn) }}:{{ stealth_vps_panel_state.port }}/{{ stealth_vps_panel_state.web_base_path }}/

URL (via SSH tunnel — recommended until UFW is configured):
    ssh -L 8888:localhost:{{ stealth_vps_panel_state.port }} root@{{ ansible_facts.default_ipv4.address | default(ansible_facts.fqdn) }}
    Then open: http://localhost:8888/{{ stealth_vps_panel_state.web_base_path }}/

Username:      {{ stealth_vps_panel_state.username }}
Password:      {{ stealth_vps_panel_state.password }}
Port:          {{ stealth_vps_panel_state.port }}
Base path:     /{{ stealth_vps_panel_state.web_base_path }}/
Service:       systemctl status x-ui

